{"type": "article", "id": 9080, "title": "牛仔布系列墨镜", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-01T08:38:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235141akS9unWROEH3CcBp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自英国的设计工作室 Mosevic 经过四年的设计和研究，推出了一款牛仔布系列的墨镜。他们用树脂材料将牛仔布融合在一起，牛仔布厚薄不等，从三层到十层都有。镜框内部为了便于清洁，使用了细致打磨过的光滑平面。而外部的牛仔布料，让它和任何一个目前的墨镜都不一样。目前产品马上就要登录 Kickstarter 众筹，现在可以来<a href=\"http://mosevic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">官方网站查看详细信息</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235138sIkS3lqTJjZ9paB1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235138cZ0VexWRyhBq1Cgo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235139a4bs5kT9WAiQNe6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235139YRfk6Fny3zpxXe7u.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235140rmzJqGBU9HYyTcxv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235140sEgaWnTYbkXeRuAd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.49511002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}